Test System API Map (Version 1.0 Freeze)
Purpose

The Test System provides developer-only tools for testing, debugging, profiling, and validating the game during development.

It never contains gameplay logic.

It never replaces managers.

It never owns game state.

It only issues requests to existing managers and utilities.

The entire subsystem can be disabled or excluded from release builds without affecting gameplay.

Folder Responsibilities

Responsible for:

Developer menu
Debug commands
Runtime cheats
Test scenarios
Performance profiling
Validation tools
Automated test helpers
Debug overlays

Not responsible for:

Gameplay
Saving
Rewards
Story progression
Board logic
Economy logic
UI gameplay
